Hun Sen Objects to Khieu Samphan , Nuon Chea Trial
PHNOM PENH , December 28 ( Xinhua ) -- Cambodia 's Prime Minister Hun Sen said Monday that he does not agree to try Khieu Samphan and Nuon Chea , the two remaining top Khmer Rouge leaders who defected to the government Friday .
Speaking at the Council of Ministers , Hun Sen stressed that it is a great event in Cambodia that Khieu Samphan and Nuon Chea defected to the Cambodian society .
They should be given a warm welcome as their defection greatly benefited the country 's peace and development , he said .
Khieu Samphan and Nuon Chea defected to the government in Pailin Friday evening and pledged to recognize Cambodia 's Constitution and the royal government led by Prime Minister Hun Sen. They also asked to be allowed to live as common people .
